### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/healthz

### Create user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{"email":"candidate@example.com"}

### Allocate ETH deposit address
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/user_000004/addresses
Content-Type: application/json

{"chain":"ETH"}

### Simulate deposit
POST http://localhost:8080/api/deposits/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id":"user_000004",
  "chain":"ETH",
  "asset":"USDT",
  "address":"ETH-deposit-user_000004",
  "amount":1000000,
  "tx_hash":"0xdeposit001"
}

### Request withdrawal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/withdrawals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id":"user_000004",
  "chain":"ETH",
  "asset":"USDT",
  "to_address":"0xreceiver",
  "amount":1000000
}

### Approve withdrawal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/withdrawals/wd_000010/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{"operator":"risk-admin"}

### Add blacklist
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/blacklist
Content-Type: application/json

{"chain":"ETH","address":"0xbad","reason":"sanctions screening hit"}

### Plan hot-to-cold collection
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/collection-tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{"chain":"ETH","asset":"USDT","threshold":500000000}

### Prometheus metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/metrics
